title: MisterMusic Show 289 NEW Indie,Alternative,Rock Radio
description:
MisterMusic Show #289 [2 hours] 192 kbps stereo -


On this week's show new music from Neon Trees, Foster the People,
Bombay Bicycle Club and another new song from indie artist Sharks and Bears off his new EP.

Plus the 'Oldie of the Week' is 11 years old, and took over the charts in the winter of 2003.  A huge modern rock hit that stayed number 1 through the entire month of January that year.

And the usual mix of indie, alternative and classics hits from the past.


It's a Rockin' Show this week.




The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS Radio.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

For recorded podcasts of the MisterMusic show, visit his podcast page http://mistermusicshow.com  Shows are updated there first every Sunday.
Or you can google search  mistermusicshow  (spelled as one word) and you'll find it.
